July 28, 2017 9:47 AM ET
Textiles, Apparel and Luxury Goods

Company Overview of Rhone Apparel, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Rhone Apparel, Inc. manufactures men’s apparel. Its products include sleeveless shirts, long sleeve shirts, short sleeve shirts, pants, and shorts. The company offers its products online. Rhone Apparel, Inc. was incorporated in 2013 and is based in New Canaan, Connecticut.


558 Old Stamford RoadNew Canaan, CT 06840United StatesFounded in 2013



Phone: 203-772-5420

rhoneapparel.com







