Learn More About Athletic Shorts for Men

Athletic Shorts Engineered for the Modern Man
Look no further for the perfect athletic shorts. Our shorts are engineered for the modern man and athlete. By using flat lock seams, power stretch material, and our SilverTech and GoldFusion technologies, we have created the perfect shorts for running, cross-training, and yoga. This allows us to to provide the best athletic shorts for men. We have shorts with built in liners to keep you comfortable and secure, amazing pockets to store media devices, hidden pockets to store away important items, and comfort waistbands to make it feel like you aren’t wearing any shorts at all. We also offer our shorts in varieties of inseam lengths.
All of our fabrics are carefully chosen specifically for the role they play in the design. We spend tremendous amounts of time testing and crafting the perfect combination of fabrics to build the perfect short. SilverTech was created to make your shorts dry faster, last longer, and stay fresher than any other shorts on the market. Typical antibacterial and anti-odor treatments used by other brands usually last for only 15-20 washes. SilverTech was permanently built into the actual fabric. GoldFusion is our brand new technology included in the liner of our Phase Shorts which has gold particles fused into the fabric. GoldFusion technology lasts longer (100 washes+) and is completely eco-friendly. 
Don’t miss out on our wide variety of men’s workout apparel including: workout pants for men and men’s workout accessories. Pair your shorts with our perfect tops featuring our: long sleeve shirts, men’s athletic tank tops, and men’s short sleeve t-shirts. Also check out our men’s gym & workout clothing collection.



Check Out Our Beginner’s Guide To Running
Running is either loved or very much hated. No matter what, it’s a part of life and one of the biggest parts of staying healthy. We break it down for you here.
